l_main_3613172\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fym1665702715516.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fym1665702715516.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fym1665702715516.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fym1665702715516\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                \n Close (CanClose) [APS]\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Window property of an application shell that determines how the application window is closed.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fym1665702715516__topic_d97583e1_d97584e1_d97585e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fym1665702715516__p_d97586e1_d97587e1_d97588e1\">CanClose\n                                   <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">On</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">Off</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">Async</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">AppShell</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"fym1665702715516__section_w1148ab1b5b3_w1149ab1b5_w1150ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Default</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1__entry__2\">\n Undefined. The default will be used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">On</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1__entry__2\">\n The user can close the application window by clicking the Close button in the title bar or choosing <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Close</span> from the system menu, or by pressing <span class=\"ph keypress\">Alt+F4</span>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Off</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1__entry__2\">\n The user can only close the application by pressing Cancel or ^Quit (Gold+Q). The Close button (if visible) is disabled.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Async</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1__entry__2\">\n The Async Interrupt trigger of the current component is activated when the application is closed.\n \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">App Shell</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11009e1_d11010e1_d11011e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The Async Interrupt trigger of the application shell is activated when the application is closed.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fym1665702715516__section_xrc_rrl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1013722e193\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fym1665702715516__table_d11012e1_d11013e1_d11014e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Caption</span> and\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">System Menu</span> must be <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fym1665702715516__section_n4j_1sl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1013722e238\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fym1665702715516__p_d97595e1_d97596e1_d97597e1\">A Close button is visible only if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">System\n               Menu</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>. If <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Close</span> is\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>, the button is disabled.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fym1665702715516__p_d97598e1_d97599e1_d97600e1\">If you choose <code class=\"ph codeph\">Asynch</code> or\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">Application Shell</code>, you need to ensure that the appropriate Async\n            Interrupt trigger contains the code to be performed when the application exits.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fym1665702715516__section_dkj_dsl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1013722e268\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"fym1665702715516__ul_v5l_fsl_4wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"fym1665702715516__li_d39614e1_d39615e1_d39616e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yye1705472567076.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yye1705472567076.html\" title=\"An application shell is the first object that is executed when a Windows or character mode application is started. It determines how the application is initialized and the first form component that is displayed.\">Application Shells for Desktop Applications</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ecw1665702715443.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>System Menu (SysMenu)</a><p>Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the Windows system menu and buttons to minimize, maximize, and close the window are available for this window. Valid values: True or False.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kno1665702715076.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Caption</a><p>Window property that determines whether the form window has a title bar. Valid values: True (default) or False.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ghq1665702608876.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger receiveMessage</a><p>Reacts to asynchronous messages that come from outside the application.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613172\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613172\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Close (CanClose) [APS] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Close (CanClose) [APS] Window property of an application shell that determines how the application window is closed. CanClose = On | Off | Async | AppShell Value Description Default Undefined. The default will be used. On The user can close the application window by clicking the Close button in the title bar or choosing Close from the system menu, or by pressing Alt+F4 . Off The user can only close the application by pressing Cancel or ^Quit (Gold+Q). The Close button (if visible) is disabled. Async The Async Interrupt trigger of the current component is activated when the application is closed. App Shell The Async Interrupt trigger of the application shell is activated when the application is closed. Usage Dynamic? No Dependencies: Caption and System Menu must be True . Description A Close button is visible only if System Menu is true . If Close is False , the button is disabled. If you choose Asynch or Application Shell , you need to ensure that the appropriate Async Interrupt trigger contains the code to be performed when the application exits. Applies to Application Shells for Desktop Applications Related Links System Menu (SysMenu) Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the Windows system menu and buttons to minimize, maximize, and close the window are available for this window. Valid values: True or False. Caption Window property that determines whether the form window has a title bar. Valid values: True (default) or False. trigger receiveMessage Reacts to asynchronous messages that come from outside the application. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}